title: 25 in. to 32 in. Adjustable Red Aluminum Emergency Sport Utility Shovel (2-Pack)
description: Lifeline's 2-Pack red color 25 in. to 32 in. Adjustable Aluminum Emergency Sport Utility Shovel is essential winter weather gear for any outdoor enthusiast who needs to dig out a car, truck, SUV, recreational vehicle, or snowmobile. 3 Piece construction easily stores in vehicle trunk for road safety preparedness. At 1.3 Lbs each, this sturdy shovel is packable for field excursions.
